  <text>
      <body>
        <div>
          <head rend="italic">A Pastorall Dialogue betwixt <hi rend="roman">Cleon</hi> and<hi rend="roman">Cælia</hi>.</head>
            <notatedMusic>
            <!-- MEI goes here -->
          </notatedMusic>
          <ab>
            <supplied reason="underlay">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <head><choice><abbr>Cho</abbr><expan>Chorus</expan></choice>.</head>
                  <stage><sp>
                    <speaker rend="italic">Cælia. Cleon.</speaker>
            <l>AS <hi rend="italic">Cælia</hi> rested in the shade</l>
            <l rend="indent1">with <hi rend="italic">Cleon</hi> by her side,</l>
            <l>the Swain thus courted the yong Mayd,</l>
            <l rend="indent1">and thus the Nimph reply'd.</l>
                  </sp></stage>
          </lg>
          <lg type="stanza">
            <stage><sp>
              <speaker rend="italic">Cleon.</speaker>
            <l>Sweet let thy captive fetters wear</l>
            <l rend="indent1">made by thine arms &amp; hands,</l>
            <l>'till such as thraldome scorn, or fear,</l>
            <l rend="indent1">envy those happy bands.</l>
            </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic">Cælia.</speaker>
            <l>Then thus my willing arms I wind</l>
            <l rend="indent1">about thee, and am so</l>
            <l>thy pris'ner, for my selfe I bind</l>
            <l rend="indent1">untill I let thee go.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l>Happy that slave whom the fair foe</l>
            <l rend="indent1">ties in so soft a chain.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l>Far happier I, but that I know</l>
            <l rend="indent1">thou <pb n="2B1v"/>wilt break loose again.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l>By thy immortal Beauties never.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent1">Fraile as thy Love's thine Oath.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l>Though beauty faile my faith lasts ever.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent1">Time will destroy them both.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l>I doat not on that snow-white skin.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent1">What then?</l>
          </sp></stage>
            <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent5">Thy purer mind.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l>It lov'd too soon.</l>
          </sp></stage>
            <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent5">Thou hadst not been</l>
            <l rend="indent1">so fair, if not so kind.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l>O strange vain fancy!</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent6">But yet true.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent1">Prove it.</l>
          </sp></stage>
            <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent5">Then make a Brade</l>
            <l>of those loose flames which circle you,</l>
            <l rend="indent1">my Sun's &amp; yet your shade.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l>'Tis done.</l>
          </sp></stage>
            <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent4">Now give it me.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
            <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
            <l rend="indent8">Thus thou.</l>
            <l rend="indent1">shalt thine own errour find;</l>
            <l>if these were Beauties, I am now</l>
            <l rend="indent1">lesse fair, because <pb n="2B2r"/>more kind.</l>
          </sp></stage>
          <stage><sp>
          <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
          <l>You shall confesse you erre, that hair,</l>
          <l rend="indent1">shall it not change the hew,</l>
          <l>or leave the golden Mountain bare?</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
           <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
           <l rend="indent1">Aye me, it is too true.</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
         <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
           <l>But this small wreath shall ever stay</l>
           <l rend="indent1">in the first native prime,</l>
           <l>and smiling when the rest decay,</l>
           <l rend="indent1">the Triumph sing of Time.</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
         <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
          <l>Then let me cut from thy fair Grove</l>
          <l rend="indent1">one branch, and let that be</l>
          <l>an Emblem of Eternall Love,</l>
          <l rend="indent1">for such is mine to thee.</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
         <speaker rend="italic">Both together.</speaker>
           <l>Thus are we both redeem'd from Time.</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
         <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
           <l rend="indent1">I, by thy grace.</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
         <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
           <l rend="indent7">And I,</l>
           <l>shall live in they immortall Rimes</l>
           <l rend="indent1">untill the Muses dy.</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
         <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
           <l>By Heav'n.</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
         <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cæl</abbr><expan>Cælia</expan></choice>.</speaker>
           <l rend="indent4">Swear not, if I must weep,</l>
           <l rend="indent1"><hi rend="italic">Jove</hi> shall not laugh at <pb n="2B2v"/>me,</l>
           <l>this kisse, my heart, and thy faith keep.</l>
         </sp></stage>
         <stage><sp>
         <speaker rend="italic"><choice><abbr>Cle</abbr><expan>Cleon</expan></choice>.</speaker>
           <l rend="indent1">This breath's my soule to thee.</l>
         </sp></stage>
        </lg>
          <lg type="stanza">
          <head><choice><abbr>Cho</abbr><expan>Chorus</expan></choice>.</head>
            <stage><sp>
              <l>Then forth the thicket <hi rend="italic">Thirsis</hi> rusht,</l>
          <l rend="indent1">where he saw all the play,</l>
          <l>the Swain stood still, and smil'd, and blush'd,</l>
          <l rend="indent1">the Nimph fled fast away.</l>
            </sp></stage>
         </lg>
          </supplied>
        </ab>
        </div>
      </body>
  </text>
